'''Pablo César''' (yavutse 26 Gashyantare 1962) ni umukinnyi wa firime wo muri [[Arijantine]]. <ref>https://vimeo.com/pablocesar</ref> <ref>https://letterboxd.com/director/pablo-cesar-1/</ref> Yagize uruhare muri sinema muri [[Afurika]] akora firime zizwi cyane ''Equinox, Ubusitani bwa Roza'', ''Los dioses de agua'' na ''Aphrodite,''mu bihugu bitandukanye bya [[Afurika]]. <ref>https://www.otroscines.com/nota?idnota=9873</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 26 Gashyantare 1962 i [[Buenos Aires]], muri [[Arijantine]] .<ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm1078506/</ref> Ni umwarimu muri Fundación Universidad del Cine Buenos Aires kuva mu 1992. <ref name="filmlinkafrica">https://filmlinkafrica.com/listing/pablo-cesar/ </ref>

== Umwuga ==
Ku myaka 6, César yatangiye gukora urwenya. Hanyuma afite imyaka 10, yanditse kandi asohora akanyamakuru ke ka mbere. Nyuma yaje kuyigurisha ku ishuri ribanza, Champagnat College. Mu 1975, musaza we José María, yamuhaye amashusho yakoresheje cyane. Hanyuma mu 1977, yanditse inyandiko akora firime ngufi. Hagati aho mu 1980, yahawe igihembo cya mbere mu cyiciro cya "Experimental" mu marushanwa ya Rosario Foto-Cine Ateneo kubera filime ye ngufi ''Del génesis'' . Filime ngufi kandi yavuzweho ibihembo byiza byo gutunganya no guhabwa igihembo cya gatatu (nta cyiciro) mubakora amafilime ya Círculo de Mar del Plata hamwe na UNCIPAR. Mu 1983, yakoze filime ''De las caras de los espejos'' maze filime yegukana igihembo cya mbere cya UNICA, Umuryango mpuzamahanga w’amafirime yabatarabigize umwuga murii uwo mwaka. 

Azwiho kuba intangarugero mu gutunganya amafilime hagati y’ibihugu byinshi na [[Arijantine]] nka [[Tuniziya]], [[Mali]], [[Bene|Benin]], [[Angola]], [[Etiyopiya]], [[Ubuhinde]] na [[Namibiya]].<ref>https://www.jcctunisie.org/jcc2017/eng/filmsDetail.php?id_film=145</ref> Mu 1991, yakoze filime yamamaye cyane yitwa ''Equinox, the Garden of the Roses'' hamwe na [[Tuniziya]]. Hanyuma mu 1996, yafatanije nu [[Buhinde]] gukora ''Unicorn,'' ''the Garden of the Fruits''. Mu 1998, yakoze firime ''Aphrodite,'' afatanya na [[Mali]].<ref>http://www.spla.pro/file.person.pablo-cesar.18272.html</ref> 

Yashyizwe kandi mu nama y'abacamanza mu birori mpuzamahanga bya firime birimo, Amiens (Ubufaransa), Iserukiramuco rya Sinema rya Montreal (Kanada), Kelibia (Tuniziya), Huy (Ububiligi), Hyderabad (Ubuhinde), FESPACO (Burkina Faso), na Villa Carlos Paz.  Mu mwaka wa 2012, yari mu ntumwa zajyanye na Perezida wa [[Arijantine]] Cristina Kirchner muri [[Angola]]. Nyuma y’amasezerano y’ubufatanye bw’umuco yashyizweho umukono na guverinoma zombi, César yayoboye filime ''The Water Gods'', ivugwa ko ari yo ya mbere yatunganijwe muri sinema hagati ya [[Arijantine]] na [[Angola]]. <ref>https://www.pagina12.com.ar/diario/suplementos/espectaculos/5-35913-2015-06-27.html</ref> <ref>https://www.todaslascriticas.com.ar/pelicula/los-dioses-del-agua/critica/pablo-suarez</ref>

Muri 2018, yayoboye film ''Pensando en él'' . <ref>https://www.deccanchronicle.com/entertainment/bollywood/120916/a-tagore-we-never-knew.html</ref> Iyi filime ishingiye ku mubano uri hagati y’umusizi w’umuhinde watsindiye Nobel witwa Rabindranath Tagore n’umwanditsi wo muri [[Arijantine]], Victoria Ocampo, ubwo basuraga [[Buenos Aires]] mu myaka ya za 1920. <ref>https://www.thecitizen.in/index.php/en/NewsDetail/index/9/12392/Argentinian-Filmmaker-Makes-Movie-on-Tagore-When-Tagore-Met-Victoria-Ocampo-in-1924</ref>

